Investigate the boat Continue your walk When you approach the boat, you see that it\'s open. Something is making quiet, suspicious noise inside. You notice a big, old knife on the ground, it\'s covered in blood. Enter the boat Grab the knife and enter the boat You leave the harbour and after few more steps you hear someone screaming, even though you know it\'s not a good idea, something is telling you to get back to harbour and check whats happening in the boat. Head back to harbour and check the boat Get back home as soon as possible First thing you notice inside is a dead woman body, lying on the floor, the noise is coming from another room. Enter another room Go back and grab the knife You open the door, immediately blurred shadow attacks you but you manage to stab creature with the knife, it jumps back and looks at you with it\'s red eyes. Attack again Run away You try to take one more step and before you move shadow attacks you with great speed, last thing you notice is long claws slashing your arm, you fall down and pass out. You reached your home safely. Scared of the recent events, you go to sleep. When you wake up next morning the whole thing seems like a very vivid dream.
